name: The Rage
description:
Title: The Rage
Size: 3508 x 4961 px
Medium: Mixed Media Digital

As 2022 is the Year of The Water-Tiger. This artwork depicts the tigers emerging from the jungles into the Lunar New Year in good stride. With all the tiger traits that are often associated with bravery, confidence, and strength. It is seen here being strengthened by the equally powerful water elements.
